                                                                                                                                    of
                                                                                                                                    e-invoicing
                                                                                                                                    systems
                                                                                                                                    for
                                                                                                                                    public
                                                                                                                                    procurement
                                                                                                                                    and
                                                                                                                                    related
                                                                                                                                    activities.
                                                                                                                                    Countrywide
                                                                                                                                    projects
                                                                                                                                    are
                                                                                                                                    launched
                                                                                                                                    by
                                                                                                                                    authorities
                                                                                                                                    with
                                                                                                                                    the
                                                                                                                                    aim
                                                                                                                                    of
                                                                                                                                    reducing
                                                                                                                                    tax
                                                                                                                                    evasion.
