                                                                                                                                    this,
                                                                                                                                    the
                                                                                                                                    Pan-European
                                                                                                                                    Public
                                                                                                                                    Procurement
                                                                                                                                    On-Line
                                                                                                                                    (PEPPOL)
                                                                                                                                    is
                                                                                                                                    a
                                                                                                                                    set
                                                                                                                                    of
                                                                                                                                    open
                                                                                                                                    standards
                                                                                                                                    and
                                                                                                                                    specifications
                                                                                                                                    which
                                                                                                                                    enables
                                                                                                                                    the
                                                                                                                                    exchange
                                                                                                                                    of
                                                                                                                                    standardised
                                                                                                                                    machine-readable
                                                                                                                                    documents
                                                                                                                                    between
                                                                                                                                    business
                                                                                                                                    partners.
