                                                                                                                                    Message
                                                                                                                                    Level
                                                                                                                                    Responses
                                                                                                                                    and
                                                                                                                                    eOrders.
                                                                                                                                    PEPPOL
                                                                                                                                    does
                                                                                                                                    in
                                                                                                                                    many
                                                                                                                                    cases
                                                                                                                                    include
                                                                                                                                    GLN
                                                                                                                                    for
                                                                                                                                    identification
                                                                                                                                    of
                                                                                                                                    economic
                                                                                                                                    operators.
                                                                                                                                    However,
                                                                                                                                    other
                                                                                                                                    identification
                                                                                                                                    systems
